body:
Namjoon’s tweet 2/26/19

“드디어 한대음에 !!

올해의 음악인, 올해의 노래, 최우수 팝, 또 문화 대상과 콘서트 부문까지. 방탄이라서 너무나 행복했습니다. 영광이고 또 감사합니다 😁😁”

[trans] “Finally at KMA !!

(Korean Music Awards)

Musician of the Year, Song of the Year, Best Pop Song, also the Culture Daesang, and even the [award of the] Concert category. I was so happy because we’re Bangtan. It’s an honor, and thank you again 😁😁”

Trans ©️ btstranslation7
